The lads know exactly what's at stake.
The idea of this club being relegated doesn't bear thinking about. The boys know what's at stake. And they know what they have to do to avoid a difficult last couple of games.

Are you still sure you'll stay up?

We're still in control of our situation.
Today was frustrating but it doesn't change anything. We still have our fate in our own hands. The boys know exactly what we need from them in the games we've got left.
We still have every chance to save ourselves next matches. I am sure the boys are well aware of how important that is.
